{"type":null,"faqId":44190,"title":"如何使用大导演","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 如果你的设备出厂时预装了大导演，打开大导演后，可以选择建立群，建立主机，让其他设备连接本机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 如果你的设备出厂时未预装大导演APK，那么只能作为从机连接了。打开大导演后，选择加入群，然后连接对应的主机</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 连接成功后，作为主机的你，可以通过下方小窗口预览到小伙伴们手机的画面</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 作为主机的你，可以在左上角的菜单里选择口令，向左移，向下移，也可以手动点击屏幕进行对焦</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5. 大导演还有自带的视频修剪，添加音乐和添加标题功能，进一步完善你的视频。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156977\" style=\"width:2.5569444in;height:4.2256947in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156978\" style=\"width:2.39375in;height:4.23125in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156979\" style=\"width:2.5569444in;height:4.265972in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156980\" style=\"width:2.3958333in;height:4.267361in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156981\" style=\"width:4.9194446in;height:3.0923612in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156982\" style=\"width:5.0590277in;height:2.8333333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9691","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400273000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":4,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"大导演,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}